{"tid":92400,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"聯合國對美國無益？美眾議員提案退聯","createTime":"2017-01-23T14:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T04:27:03.000Z","uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c248d9df27dcd932c4f26f415ddb9cc7a39ca431","tid":92400,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:21:42.000Z","msg":"2017年01月23日10:15 <br />\n<br />\n美國阿拉巴馬州眾議員羅傑斯（Mike Rogers）本月初在眾議院提出法案，建議美國退出聯合國，不過他在2015年早提過類似提案，但未獲通過。<br />\n<br />\n羅傑斯本月3日和6名議員聯名在眾院提出《2017恢復美國主權法案》，內容提及要求美國退出聯合國、不再容許聯合國把總部設在美國紐約，附加條款也包括退出世界衛生組織。<br />\n<br />\n如法案在國會兩院過關，走完流程，美國兩年後就要退出聯合國。不過這項法案並非第一次提出，過去羅傑斯的類似構想並未獲得大多數同僚支持，胎死腹中。（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170123/1041454/聯合國對美國無益？美眾議員提案退聯\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.appledaily.com.tw%2Frealtimenews%2Farticle%2Finternational%2F20170123%2F1041454%2F%E8%81%AF%E5%90%88%E5%9C%8B%E5%B0%8D%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E7%84%A1%E7%9B%8A%EF%BC%9F%E7%BE%8E%E7%9C%BE%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E6%8F%90%E6%A1%88%E9%80%80%E8%81%AF&d=8o05Qwmtv7kTVDkGQGUKkksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=ea09b812\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20170123/1041454/聯合國對美國無益？美眾議員提案退聯</a>"},{"pid":"d7e0bc09942522a677f5ba40db662261ced8e682","tid":92400,"uid":3646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:22:44.000Z","msg":"到時中國咪咩囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8ef732f0dcc667d9c033648e36c53b602b877f8","tid":92400,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T14:27:40.000Z","msg":"聯合國廢就係人都知 <br />\n點解一路咁多屆總統都唔退呢 <br />\n<br />\n因為聯合國總部係紐約 <br />\n因為有啲嘢你係要出師有名 <br />\n因為有啲嘢係要個場地去表演 <br />\n因為有啲嘢係要宣之於口 <br />\n<br />\n你估俄羅斯同中國唔想霸個會黎搞咩 <br />\n玩咩依法治世界 <br />\n係美國咁多年霸住個會 <br />\n<br />\n美國做實事從來係北約做 <br />\n聯合國係美國實力嘅表現 <br />\n為個幾個錢退聯合國 <br />\n之後再俾中俄帶班廢國黎拎搞<br />\n<br />\n侵仔咁識計數 <br />\n自己諗啦"},{"pid":"8a6ca3cca9827630a0542ff38f1aee7305aec9e5","tid":92400,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:34:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637a5cf185d5b68564c412e34336283658c9cdfa","tid":92400,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:40:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b01f12fb7a7ac4e4ccade83555c00662137bc50","tid":92400,"uid":48458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T16:56:28.000Z","msg":"唔知點解諗起學聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b60eae3cbd473da1290f314b8224fe49c891a236","tid":92400,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:00:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔知點解諗起學聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n聯, 又退聯"},{"pid":"64d81fbc5581f92ff7aa7882348bbd4a2244b5e1","tid":92400,"uid":17813,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"到時中俄玩撚曬"},{"pid":"874261de7de6f0b4f9d268f7df09b30ae2082fc0","tid":92400,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-23T17:39:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>唔知點解諗起學聯</blockquote><br />\n聯, 又退聯</blockquote><br />\n共慶歡樂退聯"},{"pid":"e2aa8e5c914f4788240c2bfd06bac1e1eb4f355b","tid":92400,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T04:59:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d123b4227176f27b45d1d40e13b987eb9022879","tid":92400,"uid":19012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:20:35.000Z","msg":"聯合國常任理事國制度都on99<br />\n<br />\n講到尾咪又係拎住核彈或準核彈既國家圍威喂"},{"pid":"df9e22e8d214467dc9267980ad819ce0d9dd3614","tid":92400,"uid":63154,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T05:34:26.000Z","msg":"聯合國如果發揮到作用，敘利亞就唔會發展到今日咁差局面"},{"pid":"140c4c5af8a657de3af4dfb2642a34a50d899713","tid":92400,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:23:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a250f6e561bb98b2ba58a0800b165d238221ee5","tid":92400,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T04:27:03.000Z","msg":"聯合國係美國打骰，中俄阻止嘅垃圾嚟"}]}